==English==

===Etymology===
Borrowed from {{bor|en|frm|paragraphe}} from {{der|en|la|paragraphus|t=sign for start of a new section of discourse}}, from {{der|en|grc|παράγραφος}}, from {{m|grc|παρά||beside}} and {{m|grc|γράφω||I write}}.

